description: Welcome To Season 12 Rookie Cup Tournament. Ingrid Mouth has had a very promising wrestling career on US so far. She bullied through Andre Shakti and today she's planning on doing the same to Sophia Locke. Sophia has limited wrestling experience but her legs are insanely strong. She plans to bulldoze over ingrid and move on in this tournament.
title: Welcome To Season 12 Rookie Cup Tournament
